Tips: Your R slot is charged by using or hitting elemental skills.
Non-Projectile skills like Yunlai Swordsmanship cannot trigger reactions.
Be careful when traversing the terrain, as the obstacles imbue elements into you.
Knockback is rare and lifesteal is removed.
